  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We may use the name you provide for your Google Profile across all of the services we offer that require a Google Account In addition we may replace past names associated with your Google Account so that you are represented consistently across all our services If other users already have your email or other information that identifies you we may show them your publicly visible Google Profile information such as your name and photo</evidence>
